// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4483 — Mass File Rename (blackbasta)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0590cbec-9c12-52e9-9250-40ecab368f50

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
